Open Money Tracker (OMT) is an accounting application. You can manage your incomes and expenses in easy way. Accounts and currency exchange rates are also available.

To help us make OMT better, please report bugs to the 4PDA forum; new feature ideas are very welcome too. Find answers or start a discussion on forum.

OMT is open source software, so everyone is encouraged to become a contributor. Non-developers can also help. For instance, you can help translate OMT, provide screenshots or blog about OMT.

OMT is released under the GNU-GPL v3 license and source code is available on GitHub.
